%%{init: {"sequence": {"messageMargin": 64, "noteMargin": 24, "boxMargin": 18, "wrap": true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Voter
    participant App as Voting App
    participant Server as API Server
    participant DB as Database

    Note over User,Server: Start: SDI lookup already completed

    User->>App: Start fingerprint check
    App->>App: Build payload
    App->>App: Encrypt payload
    App->>Server: POST /api/verify-prints<br/>(encrypted)

    Server->>Server: Decrypt + validate

    alt Single voter path (matched voter from SDI lookup)
        Server->>DB: Fetch voter by matched voter ID
        DB-->>Server: Voter record + stored fingerprint
        Server->>Server: Compare scanned vs stored
    else Collision path (candidate IDs from SDI collision)
        Server->>DB: Fetch candidate voters by candidate IDs
        DB-->>Server: Candidate records + fingerprints
        loop For each candidate
            Server->>Server: Compare scanned vs candidate
        end
        Server->>Server: Select first score >= threshold
    end

    alt Server outcome: match and not voted
        Server-->>App: 200 OK<br/>matchedVoterId + score
        App-->>User: Authentication successful
    else Server outcome: match but already voted
        Server-->>App: 400 already voted
        App-->>User: Stop and request official assistance
    else Server outcome: no fingerprint match
        Server-->>App: 400 no match<br/>score + threshold
        App-->>User: Authentication failed (retry)
    end
